    Universal bond pricing function.
    
    Parameters:
    -----------
    bond : Bond
    theta : array [lambda_0, lambda_1, beta]
    rf_curve : RiskFreeCurve
    method : str
        'auto' (default), 'analytical', or 'tree'
    
